  Brand mark: a rounded tilted-square (diamond) badge in Meshtastic green
  carrying the Meshtastic® M logomark. The 45°-rotated silhouette keeps
  MQTTastic visually distinct from the Meshtastic-Android launcher under
  every adaptive mask while staying within the brand palette.

  Canvas: 108×108dp. Geometry:
    - Diamond: vertices at (54,9), (99,54), (54,99), (9,54); 8dp rounded
      corners implemented with quadratic Béziers.
    - M logomark: source 100×55 viewport (meshtastic/design
      Mesh_Logo_Dynamic), scaled to 0.55 and centered; its farthest corner
      (|dx|+|dy| ≈ 42.6) sits comfortably inside the diamond (d = 45).
-->
